---

---

<section
    id="filosofia"
    class="py-5"
    style="background-color: var(--bg-brand); border-top: 1px solid rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.15); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.15);"
>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <!-- Main Philosophy Block -->
        <div class="row align-items-center mb-5 pb-4">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0 pe-lg-5">
                <img
                    src="/assets/img/philosophy-main.png"
                    alt="Cuidado compasivo en Bark & Co."
                    class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-lg w-100"
                    style="object-fit: cover; max-height: 600px;"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 ps-lg-4">
                <span
                    class="text-uppercase fw-bold text-success small mb-2 d-block"
                    style="letter-spacing: 0.12rem;"
                    >UN COMPROMISO CON SU BIENESTAR EMOCIONAL</span
                >
                <h2
                    class="display-5 mb-4 font-decorative text-gradient"
                    style="line-height: 1.2;"
                >
                    Nuestra filosofía Stress & Fear Free
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="mb-4"
                    style="color: #555; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 500;"
                >
                    En <strong>Bark & Co.</strong> creemos que una mascota feliz también
                    necesita sentirse segura, tranquila y emocionalmente cuidada.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-4" style="color: #555; line-height: 1.8;">
                    Por eso, cada detalle de nuestra experiencia está diseñado
                    para reducir el estrés y la ansiedad: desde la forma en que
                    interactuamos con cada mascota, hasta nuestros espacios,
                    rutinas, actividades y protocolos de socialización.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="mb-3"
                    style="color: #555; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 600;"
                >
                    Aquí, tu mascota no pasa el día bajo estrés o aislada en una
                    jaula.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-4" style="color: #555; line-height: 1.8;">
                    Juega, explora, descansa y convive en un ambiente diseñado
                    para promover calma, confianza y bienestar.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="mb-1"
                    style="color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.6;"
                >
                    Porque el verdadero cuidado no solo protege su salud física.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="mb-0"
                    style="color: var(--secondary-color); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.6;"
                >
                    También protege su tranquilidad emocional.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- How we achieve it Section -->
        <div class="pt-5 mt-5 border-top" style="border-color: rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.2) !important;">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <span class="text-uppercase fw-bold text-success small mb-2 d-block" style="letter-spacing: 0.12rem;">STRESS & FEAR FREE</span>
                <h3 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-3 font-decorative text-gradient" style="font-size: 2.4rem;">
                    ¿Cómo logramos una experiencia <span style="color: var(--secondary-color);">Stress & Fear Free?</span>
                </h3>
                <p class="text-muted mx-auto" style="max-width: 750px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                    Cada decisión, cada espacio y cada interacción están diseñados para reducir el estrés y promover el bienestar emocional de tu mascota.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-uppercase fw-semibold text-muted small" style="letter-spacing: 0.15rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">LO QUE NOS HACE DIFERENTES</span>
             <!-- 7 pillars grid -->
            <div class="d-grid gap-4 mb-5" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));">
                <!-- 1. Ambiente tipo hogar -->
                <div class="text-center px-2">
                    <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(77, 150, 124, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-house-heart" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M8 6.982C9.664 5.309 13.825 8.236 8 12 2.175 8.236 6.336 5.309 8 6.982"/>
                          <path d="M8.707 1.5a1 1 0 0 0-1.414 0L.646 8.146a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708L2 8.207V13.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3.5 15h9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V8.207l.646.647a.5.5 0 0 0 .708-.708L13 5.793V2.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v1.293zM13 7.207V13.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5V7.207l5-5z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem; min-height: 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">Ambiente tipo hogar</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3" style="line-height: 1.45; min-height: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem;">Usamos suites amplias con espacios propios y visualmente abiertos para un descanso real.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-success font-monospace" style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill mb-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-center">Más seguridad, menos ansiedad.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 2. Indoor Park climatizado -->
                <div class="text-center px-2">
                    <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(77, 150, 124, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green);">
                        <!-- Perro SVG (Lucide) -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path d="M11.25 16.25h1.5L12 17z" />
                          <path d="M16 14v.5" />
                          <path d="M4.42 11.247A13.152 13.152 0 0 0 4 14.556C4 18.728 7.582 21 12 21s8-2.272 8-6.444a11.702 11.702 0 0 0-.493-3.309" />
                          <path d="M8 14v.5" />
                          <path d="M8.5 8.5c-.384 1.05-1.083 2.028-2.344 2.5-1.931.722-3.576-.297-3.656-1-.113-.994 1.177-6.53 4-7 1.923-.321 3.651.845 3.651 2.235A7.497 7.497 0 0 1 14 5.277c0-1.39 1.844-2.598 3.767-2.277 2.823.47 4.113 6.006 4 7-.08.703-1.725 1.722-3.656 1-1.261-.472-1.855-1.45-2.239-2.5" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem; min-height: 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">Indoor Park climatizado</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3" style="line-height: 1.45; min-height: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem;">Juego y movimiento diario protegidos de climas extremos.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-success font-monospace" style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill mb-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-center">Más movimiento, mejor estado físico.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 3. Enriquecimiento diario -->
                <div class="text-center px-2">
                    <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(77, 150, 124, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green);">
                        <!-- Cerebro SVG (Lucide) -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path d="M12 18V5" />
                          <path d="M15 13a4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3-4 4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3 4" />
                          <path d="M17.598 6.5A3 3 0 1 0 12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.598 1.5" />
                          <path d="M17.997 5.125a4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77" />
                          <path d="M18 18a4 4 0 0 0 2-7.464" />
                          <path d="M19.967 17.483A4 4 0 1 1 12 18a4 4 0 1 1-7.967-.517" />
                          <path d="M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-2-7.464" />
                          <path d="M6.003 5.125a4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem; min-height: 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">Enriquecimiento diario</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3" style="line-height: 1.45; min-height: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem;">No buscamos cansar a tu perro, buscamos que se ejercite y socialice con actividades adaptadas.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-success font-monospace" style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill mb-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-center">Menos estrés, más balance.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 4. Supervisión humana real -->
                <div class="text-center px-2">
                    <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(77, 150, 124, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                          <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem; min-height: 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">Supervisión humana real</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3" style="line-height: 1.45; min-height: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem;">Veterinario en sitio, staff entrenado en protocolo Stress & Fear Free y supervisión 24/7.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-success font-monospace" style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill mb-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-center">Atención constante, tranquilidad.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 5. Socialización segura y gradual -->
                <div class="text-center px-2">
                    <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(77, 150, 124, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green);">
                        <!-- Corazón SVG (Lucide) -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem; min-height: 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">Socialización segura</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3" style="line-height: 1.45; min-height: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem;">Integraciones respetuosas y personalizadas según su temperamento y ritmo.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-success font-monospace" style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill mb-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-center">Mejores amistades, sin forzar.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 6. Ambiente diseñado para la calma -->
                <div class="text-center px-2">
                    <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(77, 150, 124, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green);">
                        <!-- Flor SVG (Lucide) -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" />
                          <path d="M12 16.5A4.5 4.5 0 1 1 7.5 12 4.5 4.5 0 1 1 12 7.5a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 4.5 4.5 4.5 4.5 0 1 1-4.5 4.5" />
                          <path d="M12 7.5V9" />
                          <path d="M7.5 12H9" />
                          <path d="M16.5 12H15" />
                          <path d="M12 16.5V15" />
                          <path d="m8 8 1.88 1.88" />
                          <path d="M14.12 9.88 16 8" />
                          <path d="m8 16 1.88-1.88" />
                          <path d="M14.12 14.12 16 16" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem; min-height: 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">Ambiente para la calma</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3" style="line-height: 1.45; min-height: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem;">Iluminación cálida, música ambiental, aromas suaves y rutinas predecibles.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-success font-monospace" style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill mb-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-center">Mayor descanso, menos estrés.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 7. Salud y bienestar integral -->
                <div class="text-center px-2">
                    <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgba(77, 150, 124, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green);">
                        <!-- Cruz de salud SVG (Lucide-style medical cross) -->
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path d="M9 21h6v-6h6V9h-6V3H9v6H3v6h6v6z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-dark" style="font-size: 0.95rem; min-height: 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">Salud y bienestar</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3" style="line-height: 1.45; min-height: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem;">Vet in-house y protocolos de bienestar para cuidar su salud física y emocional.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-success font-monospace" style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill mb-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-center">Cuidado preventivo y experto.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Bottom Benefit Box from Mockup -->
            <div class="p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 shadow-sm mx-auto mb-4" style="max-width: 950px; background-color: rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.12);">
                <div class="row g-4 align-items-stretch">
                    <!-- Left: Benefit for Dog -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 pe-md-4 benefit-divider">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center shadow-sm flex-shrink-0" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background-color: var(--accent-green); color: white;">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 640 640">
                                  <path d="M64 176C80.6 176 94.2 188.6 95.8 204.7L96.1 211.3C97.8 227.4 111.4 240 128 240L307.1 240L448 300.4L448 544C448 561.7 433.7 576 416 576L384 576C366.3 576 352 561.7 352 544L352 412.7C328 425 300.8 432 272 432C243.2 432 216 425 192 412.7L192 544C192 561.7 177.7 576 160 576L128 576C110.3 576 96 561.7 96 544L96 298.4C58.7 285.2 32 249.8 32 208C32 190.3 46.3 176 64 176zM387.8 32C395.5 32 402.7 35.6 407.4 41.8L424 64L476.1 64C488.8 64 501 69.1 510 78.1L528 96L584 96C597.3 96 608 106.7 608 120L608 144C608 188.2 572.2 224 528 224L464 224L457 252L332.3 198.6L363.9 51.4C366.3 40.1 376.2 32 387.8 32zM480 108C469 108 460 117 460 128C460 139 469 148 480 148C491 148 500 139 500 128C500 117 491 108 480 108z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-uppercase text-dark" style="font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.05rem;">EL BENEFICIO PARA TU MASCOTA</h6>
                                <p class="text-muted small mb-0" style="line-height: 1.5;">Vive días llenos de juego, compañía, descanso y atención personalizada. <span class="text-success fw-bold">Regresa a casa feliz, equilibrada y con la cola en movimiento.</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Right: Benefit for Owner -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 ps-md-4">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center shadow-sm flex-shrink-0" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); color: white;">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-heart-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 1.314C12.438-3.248 23.534 4.735 8 15-7.534 4.736 3.562-3.248 8 1.314z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-uppercase text-dark" style="font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.05rem;">Y EL BENEFICIO PARA TI</h6>
                                <p class="text-muted small mb-0" style="line-height: 1.5;">La tranquilidad de saber que está en el mejor lugar, <span class="text-success fw-bold">cuidado con amor y profesionalismo.</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Very bottom note -->
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <p class="small fw-semibold text-muted mb-0 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-2">
                    <span style="color: var(--secondary-color);">🐾</span>
                    No usamos jaulas tradicionales. Aquí, el bienestar emocional es nuestra prioridad.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .benefit-divider {
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(156, 132, 94, 0.2);
        }
    }
</style>
